: : Kup/Rodimus Prime : :

Kup: No, I dont think he has returned yet, Windlord.

Just then Rodimus flew into the base, landed and deactivated his boosters. Rodimus nearly collapsed from his wounds. He stumbled to the assembly of Maximals.

Rodimus looked down at Elita in Cam's arms, tears formed at his optics, as he took his daughter, hugging her to him.

Rodimus Prime: I have to thank you guys for not letting me get killed out there. If I did Elita would have noone, and there wouldn't be a chance of getting Nightlight back. I'm sorry I lost control, I should have dont better as commander.

He kisses Elita's forehead.
